skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: improv time
des: Say "Alexa, open Improv Time" to start with your first random question. When you're done answering, you can ask for the next question by saying "Alexa, ask me a question in Improv Time" or "Alexa, challenge me in Improv Time". Have fun getting ready for a casual conversation or warming up for your next interview, Improv Time will train you to be quick on your feet.
